<br>
Each guild gets one vote.  Simple majority wins.<br>
------------------------------------------------------------<br>
There seems to be some confusion over the 6 member per WHATEVER rule.  This vote is the clarify that rule such that everyone understands the rule.<br>
<br>
Please chose one of the following:<br>
A)You may invite whoever you wish along on your raids, as long as no more than 6 come from the same guild (whether they are a posting entity* or not).<br>
<br>
B)You may invite whoever you wish along on your raids, as long as no more than 6 come from the same posting entity*.<br>
<br>
Posting entity refers to those guilds and alliances that meet the requirements to posts dates on the calendar.<br>
------------------------------------------------------------<br>
